---
const TALLY_FORM_ID = 'nrNezl';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Submit Your Event — The Litchfield Ledger</title>
<meta name="description" content="Add your event to The Litchfield Ledger. Free submission for events happening in Litchfield County." />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=New+Amsterdam&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Libre+Baskerville:ital@0;1&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style is:global>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --green: #1e3d28;
    --green-mid: #2a5236;
    --orange: #c85c1e;
    --orange-dark: #a84a16;
    --cream: #f0ebe0;
    --cream-dark: #e4ddd0;
    --text-dark: #1a2218;
    --text-mid: #3d4f3a;
    --text-muted: #6b7d68;
  }
  body { font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: var(--cream); color: var(--text-dark); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .main-nav { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 10; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 20px 48px; }
  .nav-logo img { height: 42px; width: auto; display: block; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .nav-submit { border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5); color: white !important; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 2px; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .nav-submit:hover { border-color: white; }
  .page-hero { position: relative; height: 360px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .page-hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(10,28,14,0.65) 0%, rgba(15,35,18,0.55) 50%, rgba(8,22,12,0.78) 100%), url('/Connecticut-Mountains.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat; }
  .page-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 680px; padding: 0 24px; }
  .page-hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: white; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .page-hero-title { font-family: 'New Amsterdam', sans-serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 0.95; color: white; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .page-hero-sub { font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif; font-style: italic; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); font-size: 17px; }
  .form-wrap { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 56px 48px 80px; }
  .form-intro { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .form-intro-kicker { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--orange); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .form-intro h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .form-intro p { color: var(--text-mid); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .form-intro p + p { margin-top: 12px; }
  .form-rule { height: 1.5px; background: var(--orange); margin: 0 0 32px; max-width: 64px; }
  .tally-embed-wrap { background: white; border: 1.5px solid #c8bfa8; border-radius: 2px; padding: 24px; }
  .tally-embed-wrap iframe { width: 100% !important; border: 0 !important; display: block; min-height: 600px; }
  footer { background: var(--green); padding: 48px; text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; }
  .footer-logo-img { height: 252px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto 28px; }
  .footer-nav { margin-top: 20px; }
  .footer-nav a { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
  .footer-copy { margin-top: 20px; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
  .beehiiv-wrap { width: 100%; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .beehiiv-wrap iframe { background: transparent !important; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="main-nav">
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <img src="/orange-logo.png" alt="Litchfield Ledger" />
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/add-your-event" class="nav-submit">Submit Your Event</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <p class="page-hero-eyebrow">Submit Your Event</p>
    <h1 class="page-hero-title">Add Your Event<br>to the Ledger</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">Readings, openings, hikes, dinners, town meetings. If it's happening in the county, we want to hear about it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="form-wrap">
  <div class="form-intro">
    <div class="form-intro-kicker">How it works</div>
    <div class="form-rule"></div>
    <h2>One form. Free. No catch.</h2>
    <p>Submissions are reviewed before publication. We list events open to the public happening in Litchfield County and the surrounding northwest corner.</p>
    <p>Photos are encouraged, especially place-driven ones. The more specific the description, the better it tends to read.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tally-embed-wrap">
    <iframe
      src={`https://tally.so/embed/${TALLY_FORM_ID}?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1&dynamicHeight=1`}
      loading="lazy"
      width="100%"
      height="600"
      frameborder="0"
      marginheight="0"
      marginwidth="0"
      title="Submit Your Event"
    ></iframe>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <img src="/orange-bigblock.png" alt="The Litchfield Ledger" class="footer-logo-img" />
  <div class="beehiiv-wrap" style="margin-top: 0;">
    <script is:inline src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/v3/loader.js" data-beehiiv-form="48c597c3-c9e3-4c7a-b09b-db8627e0a48e"></script>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-nav">
    <a href="mailto:patrick@litchfieldledger.com">Contact</a>
  </div>
  <p class="footer-copy">© 2026 The Litchfield Ledger</p>
</footer>

<script is:inline src="https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js"></script>

</body>
</html>